// ── RISK AUDIT (Mk.II+ parse risk) ──────────────────────────────────
// CONFIRMED safe: effect, pure fn, ensures, comptime const, match ranges,
//   where clause, own/borrow/move, consciousness block, @evolve
// RISK: @intent(...)          → FALLBACK: verify block + comment
